<th>Element</th>
<th>Purpose</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>Primary keyword</td>
<td>What the page should rank for</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Search intent</td>
<td>Informational, commercial, or transactional</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Target audience</td>
<td>Who the content is written for</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Content outline</td>
<td>H2/H3 structure with key points</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Word count target</td>
<td>Length based on SERP analysis</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Internal links</td>
<td>Pages to link to within your site</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>External links</td>
<td>Authoritative sources to reference</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Meta title and description</td>
<td>SERP-ready title and description</td>
</tr>
<tr>
